Task-Per-Derivative: 1
Task-Section: user
Task-Description: MamoLinux desktop
Task-Extended-Description: This task provides the MamoLinux desktop environment.
Task-Key: mamolinux-desktop
Task-Seeds: desktop-minimal desktop-common

= Hardware and Architecture Support =

== Architecture-independent ==

Bluetooth:

 * (gnome-bluetooth) # desktop bluetooth support

= Network Services =

Basic network services, VPN and Windows integration.

 * (avahi-autoipd)     # IPv4 link-local interface configuration support
 * (network-manager)
 * (network-manager-config-connectivity-ubuntu)
 * (network-manager-pptp-gnome)
 * (libproxy1-plugin-gsettings)
 * (libproxy1-plugin-networkmanager)

= GUI infrastructure =

Desktop Experience:
 * (thunderbird-gnome-support)

Location Support:
 * (geoclue-2.0)

OS-only stuff:
 * (p7zip-full)            # elementary: supports a crazy number of formats

= Desktop apps =

We use many GNOME applications as part of our desktop user interface. Rather than using Debian's meta-packages they are deliberately expanded so that we can select things a bit better.

 * (thunderbird)
 * (transmission-gtk)
 * (gnome-todo)
 * (baobab)
 * (rhythmbox)
 * (cheese)
 * (totem)
 * (simple-scan)
 * (remmina)
 * (shotwell)
 * (usb-creator-gtk) [i386 amd64]
 * (deja-dup)
 * (gnome-calendar)

Accessibility tools:

 * (orca)
 * (speech-dispatcher)

Games: We only ship a few by default.
 * (aisleriot)
 * (gnome-mahjongg)
 * (gnome-mines)
 * (gnome-sudoku)
 * (branding-ubuntu)       # Ubuntu branding for some games

Default office suite: libreoffice

 * !libreoffice-core-nogui
 * (libreoffice-style-breeze)
 * (libreoffice-gnome)
 * (libreoffice-writer)
 * (libreoffice-calc)
 * (libreoffice-impress)
 * (libreoffice-math)
 * (libreoffice-ogltrans)
 * (libreoffice-pdfimport)

= Other =

 * mamolinux-desktop-minimal # we are a superset of minimal
 * mamolinux-desktop # metapackage for everything here
